sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Student
    participant API as Flask API
    participant Chat as Chat Blueprint
    participant DB as SQLite/SQLAlchemy

    Student->>API: POST /api/chat/start (student_id, uni_id)
    API->>Chat: start_chat()
    Chat->>DB: insert ChatSession
    DB-->>Chat: chat_id
    Chat-->>Student: chat session created

    Student->>API: POST /api/chat/message (chat_id, sender_id, content)
    API->>Chat: send_message()
    Chat->>DB: insert Message (user text)
    Chat->>DB: load university + faculties + programs + requirements
    Chat->>DB: load FAQ entries by uni_id
    Chat->>Chat: detect intent + score best FAQ similarity
    Chat->>DB: insert Message (bot reply)
    Chat-->>Student: smart DB-based response

    Student->>API: GET /api/chat/history/{chat_id}
    API->>Chat: get_chat_history()
    Chat->>DB: query all Message records
    DB-->>Chat: message list
    Chat-->>Student: chat history JSON
